	   <tr><td colspan=2>Slam is a natural ability of the larger races, this skill is set, iksar and wood elves come with forage and like dark elves and wood elves come with the natural ability to hide. These natural skills come with a set amount of skill, if your class does not allow progression in that skill then it stays at its natural limit. <br><br>Slam in not a typical shaman skill it is a racial skill and as such will never rise above the natural racial skill level. But it is useful in that you have a chance to interupt spell casters when you are in melee.<br>&nbsp;<br>Cannis 47 Ranger<br>Razer 42st Sk<br>Jeetkundo 20th Monk<br>Mikaraz 26th Warrior<br>Taranthian 30th Necro</td></tr>
