	   <tr><td colspan=2>Believe it or not, if you are in Greater Faydark and can't get a port to Surefall, port up to the Nexus, down to Toxx Forest, take the boat from Erudin to Qeynos and run to Halas from there.&nbsp;&nbsp;I brought my 6th level barb warrior out of Everfrost that way when I couldn't find a port.  Faster and much safer than running from Karana.  Be sure to get a SoW before running through Black Burrow, though.  You can get through BB ok, but the guards in the tunnel in Everfrost always run OUT of the tunnel.  If you aren't fast, they will follow you all the way to the McMarrins, if they don't kill you first.  Good luck, by the way<br><br>Macavitie<br>17th Northman Shaman<br>Veeshan server<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
