	   <tr><td colspan=2>I used a similar method on lower hp mobs of roughly the same level (it's called Agro Kiting btw).&nbsp;&nbsp;I found it was best to root dot and med refreshing your root every time you cast a dot.  Your med time is reduced simply because you med in battle.  Also you if you sow and regen before hand you can Can your mana up and sit while waiting for your roots to snap.  The trick is to sit far enough out to be able to stand up and cast just as the HG enters your casting range.  At 36 and so on I could solo HGs with 3 bubs of mana and the downtime with Can was small.<br>&nbsp;<br>Racknar Icerunner<br>44 Barbarian Shaman<br>&lt;Amici Loci Antiqui&gt;<br>Zeb Server</td></tr>
