	   <tr><td colspan=2>I will elaborate a little more. An Iksar has the highest penalty due to natural AC, regen, night sight, natural swimming skill. The number of bonuses your race gets from the start determines what penalty your race carries. At lvl 59 i group with a lvl 60 warrior friend and we just kill shrooms in luclin. With a fungi and regrowth I can keep it very steady and i can make roughly 1/2 a blue an hour. Yes it is that slow. If you ever get lucky enough to tag along with a say 3 wizards and a chanter (an AE group) you might get this to be a little faster but this is my option currently. <br>Iksar/troll regen post 50 is double, i currently regen at 13 points a tic with a point comming from the new luclin skills. Stack that with a fungi and regrowth it makes a huge difference.<br>Any way it seems like you cant decide what class to play based on your list of 12 and under characters so i will add this. A shaman is one of those classes that groups want/need. I started as a warrior WAAAYYY back on Karana before critical hits, class armor and some of the other things added along the way. When Karana split to terris thule i had to abandon my character and start over on Terris thule (friends all got moved when i didnt)and i made a shaman. I lovew playing a shaman and never have trouble finding something to do. We are one of a few classes that can solo post 50 very effectivly and if we can't cast it there probably is a potion equevilant we can make through alchemy. <br>(sorry for the piss poor grammer and spelling)<br>&nbsp;<br>Cantiz<br>59 Iksar Shaman<br>Edderd <br>54 Barb Warrior</td></tr>
